Key.English: ACRE is not connected to TeamSpeak!
Key.French: ACRE n'est pas connecté à TeamSpeak !
Key.Spanish: ACRE no está connectado al TeamSpeak!
Key.Italian: ACRE non è connesso a TeamSpeak!
Key.Portuguese: ACRE não está conectado ao TeamSpeak!
Key.German: ACRE ist nicht mit TeamSpeak verbunden!
Key.Japanese: ACREがTeamSpeakに接続されていません！

Key.English: ACRE PIPE ERROR: No ping return, attempting to reattach named pipe.
Key.Czech: ACRE PIPE ERROR: Žádný ping, pokus o opětovné připojení pojmenovaného potrubí.
Key.French: ERREUR DE TUNNEL ACRE : Pas de retour ping, tentative de reconnection au tunnel.
Key.Spanish: ACRE ERROR TUBERÍA: Sin ping de retorno, intentando recuperar la tubería
Key.Italian: ACRE PIPE ERROR: nessun ping di ritorno, tentativo di recuperare la pipe.
Key.Portuguese: ERRO DE TÚNEL ACRE: Sem ping de retorno, tentando reconectar ao túnel nomeado.
Key.Russian: ОШИБКА ТУННЕЛЯ ACRE: Нет ответного сигнала, попытка повторного подключения
Key.German: ACRE TUNNELFEHLER: Kein Ping empfangen, versuche Tunnel wieder zu verbinden.
Key.Japanese: ACRE PIPE ERROR: 反応が無い為、 命名済みパイプへ再接続を試みます。
Key.Chinese: ACRE 管道錯誤：Ping沒有回應，試著掛接在命名的管道重試中。
Key.Chinesesimp: ACRE通信管道错误: 通信无响应, 正在尝试重新连接
Key.Turkish: ACRE TÜNEL HATASI:Ping'e cevap dönmedi, isimli tüneli tekrar bağlamaya çalışıyor.

Key.English: ACRE has recovered from a closed pipe!
Key.Czech: ACRE se zotavil ze zavřeného PIPE!
Key.Spanish: ACRE se ha recuperado de una tubería previamente rota!
Key.Italian: ACRE si è ripreso da un pipe precedentemente chiuso.
Key.Portuguese: ACRE se recuperou de um túnel fechado!
Key.German: ACRE hat sich wieder verbunden, weiter gehts.
Key.Japanese: ACREは閉鎖済みパイプから回復しました！
Key.Chinese: ACRE 從封閉的管道恢復！
Key.Chinesesimp: ACRE已从关闭的通信管道中成功恢复
Key.Turkish: ACRE kapalı tünel hatasından başarıyla kurtuldu!
